<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8421176>
    dc:description "FIG. 1. — Homeokotorella anterioporus n. gen., n. sp. ex Taeniura lymma 1: A, B, scolex; C, metabasal armature, bothrial surface; D, basal towards metabasal armature, bothrial surface (BH and MH indicate basal and metabasal hooks, respectively); E, F, mature proglottid, in F, open circles are vitelline follicles. Scale bars: A, B, E, F, 125 µm; C, D, 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8421176/files/figure.png" ;
